# Prisma
# NOTE: prisma/migrations is intentionally NOT ignored here.
# Migration files must be tracked in source control so the database schema
# can be reproduced in production and CI/CD pipelines.
# The root .gitignore already ignores only **/prisma/migrations/**/migration.sql
# (the raw generated SQL), while keeping the migration folder structure tracked.
